  <lyrics>[V1]
 Munat Khespiyiri, Jumaruw catoksma
 Chuymajjar utt'asim wiñayataqui;
 Munasihaniampi thaquiman irpita,
 Jan khepar uñtasaw nayajj arcama.
 
[C]
  Take chuymajjampiw nayajj yupaycháma,
 Juman sutimatsa nayajj khanancha;
 Má thuru cruzana wilam wartasawa,
 Khespiyañ altajja takenitaqui.
 
[V2]
 Maypach jacáwejja Jumaruw catuysma
 Chek iyawsañampi jacañataqui;
 Kollan Ajayumajj chuymajjanay akpan,
 Mojjsa arunacam parlañataqui.
 
[V3]
 Cunapachatejja Supayajj jutani,
 Cunayman yant'ampi mayjt'ayañatac;
 Jurnan ch'amamampejj jan ajjsarasawa
 Nayajj atipjájja. Cristo Tatitu.
 
[V4]
 Tatit Jesucristo, take chuymajjampi
 Cruzam apt'atawa nayajj arcama.
 T'akhesiñas jutpan, llaquisiñanacas,
 Jumaw imitata munasiñampi.
 
 </lyrics></song>